The version of Microsoft Internet Explorer 8 available at the time of writing has numerous issues when it comes to rendering vBulletin pages correctly.<br />
<br />
Thankfully, Microsoft has provided a means that allows developers to instruct IE8 to render pages in the way that IE7 does.<br />
<br />
Switching this option to 'Yes' will cause IE8 to behave like IE7, eliminating the IE8 page rendering problems.